channel.title: Searching for partnet in crime! ;)
channel.description:
I have finally found a base and source with a pretty nice client I'd like to start off with.
It is a zepsity base.. yes I know. Actually this source has had ALOT of work done within' it and is doing great!
I decided I would like a partner to code with. Whether it is over Skype™, Teamviewer™, or something else.
To do this, and for it to work.. we would have to live around the same time zones. I live: (-6) Central Time in Texas, United States of America
For this, it would be great to have a team member (partner) to work with and help each other with coding when we get stuck, and also to have two different opinions when it comes to certain things.
Thanks -KTHillman
----------------------
Skype: "kyle.thomas.hillman" Other: PM ME FOR OTHER ARRANGEMENTS IF YOUR INTERESTED!
